Package: tamatoamlr
Title: Analyze and Visualize US AMLR Pinniped Data
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
        c(person("Sam", "Woodman", email = "sam.woodman@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6071-8186")),
        person("Karen", "Snyder", email = "ksnyder@g.hmc.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: This package contains Tamatoa, a Shiny app that connects to the 
    US AMLR Pinniped database, 
    and allows users to analyze and visualize data from this database.
    There are some exported functions that are helpful for processing 
    US AMLR Pinniped data for more familiar users, but the intent
    is for the Shiny app to provide the main functionality for this package.
License: Apache License (== 2)
